title: [The Finest Hour, Menswear]
description: Brilliant reds and darker wine hues dominate this side of the tent, the room holding the faintest scent of spice.  Burgundy carpet covers the floor, complementing a dark mahogany wardrobe wardrobe that rests in a corner of the space.  The same polished wood was used to craft an elegantly scrolled rack that holds various footwear.
